{"schema":{"type":"object","description":"Credential metadata — secret values are always masked","properties":{"id":{"type":"string","example":"01HX9QRPBZW4EZG3BTYV7K0M5C"},"name":{"type":"string","example":"acme-sftp-key"},"credentialType":{"type":"string","description":"Type of credential secret","enum":["SSH_KEY","PASSWORD","API_TOKEN","AWS_ACCESS_KEY","AZURE_SAS","GCP_SERVICE_ACCOUNT","OAUTH2_CLIENT"],"example":"SSH_KEY","title":"CredentialType"},"username":{"type":"string","nullable":true,"example":"sftp-user"},"maskedValue":{"type":"string","description":"Last 4 chars of secret, rest masked — e.g. \"****KEY\"","example":"****KEY"},"createdAt":{"type":"string","format":"date-time","example":"2024-03-15T08:00:00Z"},"updatedAt":{"type":"string","format":"date-time","example":"2024-03-15T09:30:00Z"},"rotatedAt":{"type":"string","format":"date-time","nullable":true,"example":null}},"title":"CredentialResponse"},"schemaType":"response"}